The paper deals with the analysis of channel impulse responses in molecular communication, which involves the release of molecules as information carriers. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and neural networks (cs.NE), as well as simulation and modeling (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and systems and control (cs.SY).
